'From Squeak3.2alpha of 3 October 2001 [latest update: #4530] on 21 November 2001 at 4:20:45 pm'!"Change Set:		viewerAddPrelude-swDate:			21 November 2001Author:			Scott WallaceAdvance arrival of a couple of methods that help solve an annoying order problem in a forthcoming update."!!Morph class methodsFor: 'scripting' stamp: 'sw 11/15/2001 12:16'!additionsToViewerCategoryDragAndDrop	"Answer viewer additions for the 'drag & drop' category"	^#(		#'drag & drop' 		(			(slot dropEnabled 'Whether drop is enabled' Boolean readWrite Player getDropEnabled Player setDropEnabled:)			(slot sticky 'Whether this is sticky' Boolean readWrite Player getSticky Player setSticky:)			(slot resistsRemoval 'Whether this is resistant to easy removal via the dismiss or grab halo handles' Boolean readWrite Player getResistsRemoval Player setResistsRemoval:)				))! !!Morph class methodsFor: 'scripting' stamp: 'sw 11/16/2001 10:21'!additionsToViewerCategoryLayout	"Answer viewer additions for the 'layout' category"	^#(		layout 		(			(slot clipSubmorphs 'Whether or not to clip my submorphs' Boolean readWrite Player getClipSubmorphs Player setClipSubmorphs:)		))! !